Talk about your bad days.

486
00:38:02,203 --> 00:38:04,967
Stop it!
<i>I wish I could.</i>

487
00:38:05,039 --> 00:38:07,166
Fiscal year's ending,

488
00:38:07,241 --> 00:38:10,836
