Julian's waiting.

495
00:38:29,897 --> 00:38:32,661
[Whispering]
No, he's not.

496
00:38:32,733 --> 00:38:36,032
- How did you do that?
- <i>She didn't.</i>

497
00:38:36,103 --> 00:38:40,437
